CHANGES
=======

0.1.12
------

* Insure unicode file names are correctly encoded/decoded
* Bugfix: symlink source must be relative to the destination path

0.1.11
------

* Fallback using symlink on OSError

0.1.10
------

* Unit testing filename based timestamp and name collision handling
* Make symlinks on error to support execution over NFS

0.1.9
-----

* Fix wrong date/time offset on videos generated by some Android devices

0.1.8
-----

* Bugfix: continue processing if exiftool is not available

0.1.7
-----

* Support for non destructive operations

0.1.6
-----

* Support for more time sources!

0.1.5
-----

* Support for TIFF file format

0.1.4
-----

* Case insensitive file extension filtering

0.1.3
-----

* Better rendering of the command line tool help

0.1.2
-----

* Fix timezone issue and add integration test

0.1.1
-----

* Bugfixing: Pictures were "moved" in albums instead of being linked

0.1.0
-----

* New build configuration for Travis CI
* Now with ical driven album creation!
* Main structure and basic support for timeline management
